---

#### Paint-like program. ( The Gimp is too heavy for little image manipulations)
~~~sh

apt-get install pinta
~~~


#### Games
~~~sh

wesnoth openarena freeciv freeorion 
~~~

#### Ruby setup
~~~sh

apt-get install curl
gpg --keyserver hkp://keys.gnupg.net --recv-keys 409B6B1796C275462A1703113804BB82D39DC0E3
curl -sSL https://get.rvm.io | bash -s stable
# Should restart terminal to reload ~/.profile or ~/.bashrc
rvm install 2.0
~~~
